erms."}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-4 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed","children":"As Presenze is currently under active development, this policy may be updated before public release. We will notify users of any significant changes."}]]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"mb-12","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white","children":"Information We Collect"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-4 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed","children":"We collect only the information necessary to operate the Presenze platform:"}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"mt-4 space-y-3 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400","children":[["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"className":"text-slate-900 dark:text-white","children":"Account Information:"}]," Name, email address, institutional role (student, faculty, HOD, admin), and authentication credentials."]}],["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"className":"text-slate-900 dark:text-white","children":"Attendance Data:"}]," Bluetooth proximity verification records, session timestamps, classroom assignments, and attendance history."]}],["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"className":"text-slate-900 dark:text-white","children":"Academic Information:"}]," Course enrollments, subject allocations, department assignments, timetable data, and section information."]}],["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"className":"text-slate-900 dark:text-white","children":"Device Information:"}]," Bluetooth identifiers (for session verification), device type, and operating system version to ensure compatibility."]}],["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"className":"text-slate-900 dark:text-white","children":"Usage Data:"}]," App interactions, feature usage patterns, and error logs to improve platform performance."]}]]}]]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"mb-12","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white","children":"How We Use Information"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-4 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed","children":"We use collected information to:"}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"mt-4 space-y-3 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400","children":[["$","li",null,{"children":"Verify attendance through Bluetooth Low Energy proximity detection"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Manage user accounts and role-based access permissions"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Generate attendance reports and analytics for administrators"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Synchronize data between mobile apps and the Admin Portal"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Send important notifications about sessions, timetables, and platform updates"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Improve platform performance, security, and user experience"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Provide customer support and respond to user inquiries"}]]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-4 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed","children":"We do not sell your personal information to third parties. We do not use your data for advertising purposes."}]]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"mb-12","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white","children":"Data Security"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-4 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed","children":"We protect your data using industry-standard security practices:"}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"mt-4 space-y-3 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400","children":[["$","li",null,{"children":"Encrypted data transmission using HTTPS/TLS protocols"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Secure authentication and session management"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Role-based access controls to limit data exposure"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Regular security audits and vulnerability assessments"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Secure cloud infrastructure with Supabase and modern backend practices"}]]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-4 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed","children":"While we implement strong security measures, no system is completely secure. We continuously work to improve our security practices as the platform evolves."}]]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"mb-12","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white","children":"Third-Party Services"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-4 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed","children":"Presenze uses the following third-party services to operate the platform:"}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"mt-4 space-y-3 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400","children":[["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"className":"text-slate-900 dark:text-white","children":"Supabase:"}]," Database and authentication infrastructure"]}],["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"className":"text-slate-900 dark:text-white","children":"Cloud Hosting Providers:"}]," For backend services and data storage"]}]]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-4 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed","children":"These services have their own privacy policies and security practices. We carefully select partners that meet high standards for data protection."}]]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"mb-12","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white","children":"Data Retention"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-4 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed","children":"We retain your data as long as your account is active and for a reasonable period afterward to comply with institutional record-keeping requirements. Attendance records are typically retained for the duration of your academic enrollment plus an additional period as required by your institution."}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-4 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed","children":"You may request deletion of your personal data by contacting us. We will honor such requests unless we are required to retain data for legal or legitimate operational reasons."}]]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"mb-12","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white","children":"Children's Privacy"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-4 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed","children":"Presenze is designed for use by educational institutions and their enrolled students, faculty, and administrators. We do not knowingly collect information from children under 13 without appropriate parental or institutional consent. If you believe we have collected such information inappropriately, please contact us immediately."}]]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"mb-12","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white","children":"Changes to This Policy"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-4 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed","children":"As Presenze is under active development, we may update this Privacy Policy to reflect changes in our practices, platform features, or legal requirements. Significant changes will be communicated to users via email or in-app notifications. Continued use of Presenze after changes indicates acceptance of the updated policy."}]]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"mb-12","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white","children":"Contact Information"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-4 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed","children":"If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or how we handle your data, please contact us:"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-6 dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-white/5","children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"te